paper_abstract: A Fredholm second kind integral equation (SKIE) formulation is constructed for the Dirichlet problem of the biharmonic equation in three dimensions. A fast numerical algorithm is developed based on the constructed SKIE. Its performance is illustrated via several numerical examples. (C) 2011 Elsevier Inc. All rights reserved.
paper_title: Second kind integral equations for the first kind Dirichlet problem of the biharmonic equation in three dimensions
